## Get referral code
> Request example

```shell
curl 'https://<%= config[:api_endpoint] %>/loyalty/referral/code?shop_id=SHOP_ID&shop_secret=SHOP_SECRET&identifier=PHONE'
```

> The above command returns JSON structured like this:

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "payload": {
    "message": "Success",
    "codes": [
      {
        "referral_program_id": 1,
        "code": "XXX-YYY-ZZZ",
        "description": "..."
      },
      {
        "referral_program_id": 2,
        "code": "#mastermain",
        "description": null
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

Method returns member's referrer code.

### HTTP Request

`GET https://<%= config[:api_endpoint] %>/loyalty/referral/code`

### Query Parameters

| Parameter   | Required | Description                |
|-------------|----------|----------------------------|
| shop_id     | true     | Your API key               |
| shop_secret | true     | Your API secret key        |
| identifier  | true     | User's phone (identifier)  |





